reviewText: Terrible low quality old footage, turned it off after a few minutes

I enjoyed the retrospective of a sport I have grown to love.....
May the adventure never be forgotten. Thanks guys!
If you love paddling this movie gives you an appreciation for the sport. Vintage photo, home movies really documents the history of the sport.
Great look backward at paddling on the river and the awesome pioneers of this sport. Very well done and entertaining, not to mention excellent photography.
Definitely A Good One To Add To Any Whitewater Enthusiasts Library. It's Great To See & Learn How The Sport Evolved. I Enjoyed This Video.
